OL,3,CTwo dead and dozens injured after tram
OL,4,Cderails in Milan
OL,6,FA tram derailed and crashed into a
OL,7,Fbuilding in Milan on Friday, killing
OL,8,Ftwo people and injuring 38 others.
OL,10,FOne of the dead was hit by the tram as
OL,11,Fit derailed, and another was a
OL,12,Fpassenger, the city's mayor, Beppe
OL,13,FSala, said.
OL,15,FNone of those injured was in a life-
OL,16,Fthreatening condition, he added.
OL,18,FDozens of ambulances, fire trucks and
OL,19,Fpolice cars responded to the crash,
OL,20,Fwith crews escorting passengers in
OL,21,Fthermal blankets away from the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
