OL,3,CTwo dead and dozens injured after tram
OL,4,Cderails in Milan
OL,6,FThe No.9 tram, which runs through the
OL,7,Fheart of Italy's financial capital,
OL,8,Fhit a building after travelling down
OL,9,FVittorio Veneto avenue at high speed.
OL,11,FIt was supposed to continue straight
OL,12,Falong the road, but it suddenly
OL,13,Fswerved at a switch track used by
OL,14,Fanother tram line and went off its
OL,15,Fusual course, according to video of
OL,16,Fthe crash broadcast by Sky TG24.
OL,18,FThe video shows the tram nearly
OL,19,Fflipping onto its side as it takes the
OL,20,Fcurve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
