OL,3,CTwo dead and dozens injured after tram
OL,4,Cderails in Milan
OL,6,FATM, the Milan public transport
OL,7,Fcompany, said it was cooperating with
OL,8,Fprosecutors "to precisely establish
OL,9,Fthe cause and dynamic of the incident."
OL,11,FMilan has just hosted the 2026 Winter
OL,12,FOlympics and is preparing to host the
OL,13,FParalympics. The city is currently
OL,14,Fstaging Milan Fashion Week.
